00:20:28,430 --> 00:20:29,840
是关于总统的事
It's a story about the president.

338
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:31,950
你没听到我说什么吗
Did you not hear me the first time?

339
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:39,480
我认为在你的烧烤店里...曾发生过一些事
I think things happened... in your barbecue place.

340
00:20:40,120 --> 00:20:41,240
会面
Meetings.

341
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:42,670
你可能顺耳听到过什么
Things you might have overheard.

342
00:20:44,350 --> 00:20:46,250
我觉得总统触犯了法律
I think the president broke the law,

343
00:20:46,470 --> 00:20:47,990
而且我觉得你知情
and I think you know about it.

344
00:20:50,010 --> 00:20:53,000
跟我来  找个没人能听到的地方再聊
Come with me. Let's talk where no one can hear us.

345
00:21:07,860 --> 00:21:11,450
-你带录音笔了吗  -带了
