叫"我从来没有过"
called Never Have I Ever.

468
00:29:20,150 --> 00:29:23,220
-知道那游戏吗  -有过那个经历就喝
- You know that game? - You drink when you have.

469
00:29:24,380 --> 00:29:25,550
就是那个
That's the one.

470
00:29:28,270 --> 00:29:30,080
或者如果总统有过
Or if the President has.

471
00:29:41,190 --> 00:29:43,600
被特别检察官调查的时候
Never have I ever perjured myself

472
00:29:43,600 --> 00:29:45,880
我从来没有做过伪证
when investigated by a special prosecutor.

473
00:29:58,310 --> 00:30:01,290
我从来没有和雷蒙德·塔斯克达成过协议
Never have I ever struck a deal with Raymond Tusk...

474
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:05,880
让他做伪证换取赦免
to perjure himself in exchange for a pardon.

475
00:30:14,760 --> 00:30:17,570
我从来没有密谋弹劾过总统
Never have I ever conspired to impeach a President

476
00:30:17,570 --> 00:30:19,890
好让我自己当上总统
so I could become President myself.

477
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:42,000
我们得再叫点酒了
We're gonna need more beer.

478
00:30:49,980 --> 00:30:52,660
-第一夫人在1号线上  先生  -谢谢
- The First Lady is on line one, sir. - Thank you.

479
00:30:58,490 --> 00:30:59,200
克莱尔
Claire.

480
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:02,320
道格给我打电话说我们要派出自己的军队
Doug called me about sending in our own troops.

481
00:31:02,700 --> 00:31:06,160
要么派出要么无所行动  康威不肯让步
