00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:46,640
我们俩决定这样最好
We both decided it was for the best.

495
00:31:49,270 --> 00:31:51,400
我们不用担心他  弗兰西斯
We don't have to worry about him, Francis.

496
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:55,660
